rows.name:
It's like a dream. I never thought I'd be
living together with my kids again...

rows.label: tlk4171015101_msg0002
rows.name:
If it hadn't have been for you and Elnoth,
I don't know what I would have...

rows.label: tlk4171015101_msg0003
rows.name:
Even once Elnoth's back from the empire,
I intend to do some earnest work for
once and we'll live like a real family.
